@baseUrl = http://localhost:5000
@tenantId = 00000000-0000-0000-0000-000000000001
@username = admin
@password = P@ssw0rd!

### 1. Login to get token (Execute this first)
# @name login
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/auth/token
Content-Type: application/json
X-Tenant-Id: {{tenantId}}

{
  "username": "{{username}}",
  "password": "{{password}}"
}

###
@accessToken = {{login.response.body.$.data.accessToken}}

### 1.1 获取 Anti-Forgery Token
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}
X-Tenant-Id: {{tenantId}}

###

### 2. 查询审计日志列表（分页）
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/audit?pageIndex=1&pageSize=10
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}
X-Tenant-Id: {{tenantId}}

### 2.1 按行为与结果过滤
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/audit?pageIndex=1&pageSize=20&action=CLIENT_ERROR&result=Failure
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}
X-Tenant-Id: {{tenantId}}

### 2.2 上报前端异常（CLIENT_ERROR）
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/audit/client-errors
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}
X-Tenant-Id: {{tenantId}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "message": "TypeError: Cannot read properties of undefined",
  "stack": "TypeError: ...",
  "url": "http://localhost:5173/settings/audit",
  "component": "AuditPage",
  "level": "error"
}

### 3. 查询审计日志列表（第2页）
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/audit?pageIndex=2&pageSize=10
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}
X-Tenant-Id: {{tenantId}}

### 4. 查询审计日志列表（每页20条）
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/audit?pageIndex=1&pageSize=20
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}
X-Tenant-Id: {{tenantId}}

### 5. 登录失败测试（触发审计日志记录）
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/auth/token
Content-Type: application/json
X-Tenant-Id: {{tenantId}}

{
  "username": "{{username}}",
  "password": "WrongPassword@123"
}

### 6. 修改密码（触发审计日志记录）
PUT {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/auth/password
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}
X-Tenant-Id: {{tenantId}}

{
  "currentPassword": "{{password}}",
  "newPassword": "{{password}}",
  "confirmPassword": "{{password}}"
}

### 7. 退出登录（触发审计日志记录）
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/auth/logout
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}
X-Tenant-Id: {{tenantId}}

### 8. 重新登录以查看新的审计日志
# @name login2
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/auth/token
Content-Type: application/json
X-Tenant-Id: {{tenantId}}

{
  "username": "{{username}}",
  "password": "{{password}}"
}

###
@accessToken2 = {{login2.response.body.$.data.accessToken}}

### 9. 查询最新的审计日志（应包含登录失败、密码修改、退出登录等记录）
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/audit?pageIndex=1&pageSize=50
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken2}}
X-Tenant-Id: {{tenantId}}

### 10. 验证审计日志内容完整性
# 手动检查响应中的审计记录应包含：
# - Actor: 操作人（用户名）
# - Action: 操作类型（LOGIN, LOGOUT, CHANGE_PASSWORD等）
# - Result: 操作结果（SUCCESS, FAILED, LOCKED等）
# - IpAddress: IP地址
# - UserAgent: 用户代理
# - OccurredAt: 发生时间
# - ClientType, ClientPlatform, ClientChannel, ClientAgent: 客户端信息

### 11. 测试分页参数边界值
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/audit?pageIndex=1&pageSize=100
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken2}}
X-Tenant-Id: {{tenantId}}

### 12. 测试小分页（每页1条）
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/audit?pageIndex=1&pageSize=1
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken2}}
X-Tenant-Id: {{tenantId}}

